data.name: infoText1.Text
data.value: To the left is a simplified diagram of DES. The main sections of the algorithm that we will exploit with Linear Cryptanalysis are the S-boxes, so for the purposes of a more simplified diagram we have removed elements that are already considered linear.

data.name: infoText2.Text
data.value: Your task, should you choose to accept it is to determine the value of K1 and K2. Linear Crypanalysis is an attack in which you as an attacker possess mulitple Plain Text/Cipher Text pairs. You will use this information along with the power of math to identify relationships between the Pre-Round Text and Post-Round Text.
